investigation.title: International Space Station - Microbial Observatory of Pathogenic Virus, Bacteria, and Fungi project
investigation.description: This study investigated the interplay between the microbial community of the International Space Station and its crew. Environmental samples were collected from 8 habitable locations around the ISS.
